---
title: Teriyaki Veggie Stir-Fry & Ginger Rice with Japanese Mayo & Fried Egg
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan for a sweet and savoury teriyaki glaze that can take a veggie stir-fry to stardom. Sealing this stir-fry’s rightful place is a perfectly cooked fried egg - we give it a gold star for sure!

*We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with baby broccoli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
